These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, bartender
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, thai
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, trike
1. the bartender is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
2. the videographer is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk      | coffee    |
| Job           | bartender | videographer |
| Nationality   | canadian       | thai  |
| Transport     | train      | trike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peas, asparagus
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, country
2 different pets are kept: hamster, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | asparagus | peas |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | country         |
| Pet           | snake     | hamster         |
| Transport     | taxi    | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, paramedic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, trance
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, airplane
1. the fan of trance is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | reading          | fishing |
| Job           | paramedic | software-developer     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz            | trance         |
| Transport     | airplane         | tram   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
