.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, peach
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, ambient
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person eating cucumber is the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola |
| Food          | peach   | cucumber |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | electronic     |
| Transport     | quad-bike | bus     |

 